1ï¸âƒ£ Security Review Checklist (Bank / Regulated-Grade)

You can literally paste this into a Security Review / Threat Model doc.


---

A. Authentication & Authorization

âœ… Identity Ownership

[ ] Host platform is the single source of truth for user identity

[ ] No user credentials stored or handled by BG system

[ ] Platform token is never exposed to frontend


âœ… BG-Scoped Authorization

[ ] BG Session Token is scoped to single BG reference

[ ] Token contains bg_ref, winame, requestId

[ ] Token cannot be reused for another BG


âœ… Token Hygiene

[ ] Short-lived token (â‰¤ 15 minutes)

[ ] Token revoked on submit / cancel

[ ] Replay protection via jti



---

B. API Security

âœ… Ingress Validation

[ ] All backend APIs require BG session token

[ ] Token validated on every request

[ ] Missing / invalid token returns 401


âœ… Authorization Checks

[ ] BG_READ enforced for fetch APIs

[ ] BG_WRITE enforced for submit API

[ ] Scope escalation not possible


âœ… Platform Trust Boundary

[ ] Platform token validated server-side only

[ ] No platform secrets stored in frontend

[ ] Optional callback validation supported



---

C. Data Protection

âœ… Data in Transit

[ ] TLS 1.2+ enforced end-to-end

[ ] No plaintext BG data in headers

[ ] BG text only sent in request body


âœ… Data at Rest

[ ] BG drafts encrypted at rest (if stored)

[ ] Final BG text stored with checksum / hash

[ ] No raw BG stored in logs



---

D. Session & State Management

âœ… Session Control

[ ] Session bound to sessionID

[ ] Multiple tabs handled safely

[ ] Stale sessions rejected


âœ… Duplicate Protection

[ ] Submit API is idempotent

[ ] Duplicate submit returns 409

[ ] BG state locked after submission



---

E. Logging & Audit

âœ… Audit Trail

[ ] Token issuance logged

[ ] BG submit logged with timestamp

[ ] User + BG reference captured


âœ… Secure Logging

[ ] No tokens logged

[ ] No BG text logged

[ ] Error logs sanitized



---

F. Error Handling

âœ… Safe Error Responses

[ ] No internal stack traces exposed

[ ] Business errors mapped to codes

[ ] Security errors generic (Unauthorized, not â€œJWT expired atâ€¦â€)



---

G. Compliance & Review

[ ] OWASP API Top 10 reviewed

[ ] Pen-test ready endpoints identified

[ ] Secrets rotated via vault / env vars

[ ] Architecture approved by platform team



---

âœ… Security Review Verdict

> BG system follows least privilege, short-lived authorization, and clear trust boundaries.




